@*
    Minimal chrome for anonymous Account/* pages (Login, Logout, AccessDenied).
    We deliberately do NOT mount the MainLayout/MudAppBar here:
      - It pulls in dozens of MudBlazor nav icons that flash full-page-large before
        component CSS settles, and renders broken when the user is unauthenticated
        (AuthorizeView fallbacks expand giant inline SVGs).
      - It triggers AuthorizeView lookups + extra policy round-trips on a page where
        the only goal is to collect credentials.
    MudThemeProvider / MudPopoverProvider / etc. are already mounted at the Routes level
    so MudBlazor styles still work for any controls used inside <Body/>.
*@
@inherits LayoutComponentBase

<main class="mi-auth-shell">
    @Body
</main>
